{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban anonymous SIM cards and require ID verification for all SIM sales in the UK",
        "additional_details": "SIM cards can currently be purchased from some shops without providing identification. This may allow anonymous phone numbers to be used for scam calls, fraud, harassment, and other criminal activities.\r\n\r\nRequiring ID verification when purchasing or activating a SIM card could help improve accountability, support law enforcement investigations, and help reduce misuse of mobile networks.",
        "background": "Introduce legislation requiring mobile network providers and retailers to verify valid identification before selling or activating any SIM card, including prepaid SIM cards.",
